c.name: Friendship and Love
c.n: The day I fell in love with you is the day I felt alive again. Thank you for making me feel so alive.The day I fell in love with you is the day I felt alive again. Thank you for making me feel so alive.
I could search my whole life and through and never find another you.I could search my whole life and through and never find another you.
Without you I am nothing; with you I am everything.Without you I am nothing; with you I am everything.
A day without your love is a day without life.A day without your love is a day without life.

The best and most beautiful things in the world can't be seen, nor touched, but are felt in the heart.The best and most beautiful things in the world can't be seen, nor touched, but are felt in the heart.
Just wanted you to know that someone is thinking of you! Just wanted you to know that someone is thinking of you!
Words aren't enough to tell you how wonderful you are. I love you.Words aren't enough to tell you how wonderful you are. I love you.
Have a great day at work! I'm counting down till you get home.Have a great day at work! I'm counting down till you get home.
You are my one of a kind. Feeling so blessed!You are my one of a kind. Feeling so blessed!
"The best thing to hold onto in life is each other." - Audrey Hepburn"The best thing to hold onto in life is each other." - Audrey Hepburn
You are always there for me and so you give me the courage to stand alone.You are always there for me and so you give me the courage to stand alone.

As you admire the wonderful things God has made today, remember you're one of them. You're special. You're loved. Loved by me!As you admire the wonderful things God has made today, remember you're one of them. You're special. You're loved. Loved by me!

I want to be your favorite hello, and hardest goodbye.I want to be your favorite hello, and hardest goodbye.

Being with you is like having every single one of my wishes come true.Being with you is like having every single one of my wishes come true.
I love you more today than I did yesterday, but not as much as I will tomorrow!I love you more today than I did yesterday, but not as much as I will tomorrow!
I love you, not for what you are, but for what I am when I am with you.I love you, not for what you are, but for what I am when I am with you.
A hundred hearts would be too few to carry all my love for you.A hundred hearts would be too few to carry all my love for you.
